{%- if handle == 'auction-tenanted-property-pre-sale-legal-pack' or handle == 'auction-legal-pack' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}Complete legal documentation pack for property auctions, including all required searches, title documents, and certificates. Everything your solicitor needs — prepared and ready for auction day.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'listing-boost-survey-photography-service' or handle == 'rics-level-2-survey' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}Professional RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Survey combined with high-quality property photography and a listing boost across major UK portals. One order, three essential services.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'outlays' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}We handle all search fees, Land Registry charges, and local authority costs on your behalf. Pay upfront with full transparency — no hidden fees, no surprises at completion.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'photography-service' or handle == 'professional-photography' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}High-quality property photography to showcase your property at its very best. Professional interior and exterior shots, edited and optimised for all major listing portals.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'property-title' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}Official Land Registry title deeds and title plans for any property in England & Wales. Verify ownership, check restrictions, and get the documents you need — delivered digitally.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'rent-increase-service' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}Legally compliant Section 13 rent increase notices drafted and served correctly on your behalf. We handle the paperwork so you can increase your rental income with confidence.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'tenancy-agreement' -%}
  {%- capture service_desc -%}Professionally drafted AST agreements compliant with current UK housing legislation. Customised to your property and terms — ready to sign and use immediately.{%- endcapture -%}
{%- elsif handle == 'boosting-listing' -%}
